path = '/data/BCI-CRC/SO/data/CRC_multiome/ArchR_final_analysis/Matrices/ArchRmatrices_allCells/'
matrix = 'motifMatrix'
adataMM = sc.read_mtx(path + matrix + '.mtx').T

features = pd.read_csv(path + matrix + '_features.csv', )
adataMM.var_names = features['x'].str.split('_', expand=True)[0]

barcodes = pd.read_csv(path + matrix + '_barcodes.csv', )
adataMM.obs_names = barcodes['x']

adataMM = adataMM[adata.obs_names,]
adataMM.obs = adata.obs.copy()

adataMM.obsm['X_umap'] = adata.obsm['X_umap']

adataMM.obsm['X_WNN'] = adata.obsm['X_WNN']
